Abalwadde balina omuwendo gwa ssero eryeru (ng'okusingira ddala obutoffaali bw'omusaayi) omutono oba ogutono mu mitendera egyasooka.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obulwadde bwa lymphopenia obuli n'omuwendo gwa ssero eryeru lya ssero 4 × 109/L n'omuwendo gwa ssero ly'omusaayi 1 × 109/L, wamu n'omutindo omunene ogwa aspartate aminotransferase n'omusaayi ogusirikka, byazuulibwa mu balwadde 1,099 abalina COVID-19.
