Obulwadde bwa COVID-19 buyinza okulabika mu bantu abasinga obungi nga buliko obubonero obutali bumu obw'ekisenge oba obweru bw'amabala mu biwundu.
Abalwadde batera okufuna omusujja gw'amawuggwe, obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'amawuggwe, n'obulwadde bw'okufuna obuzibu obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu (Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome, ARS).
Mu ARDS, obulwadde obwo buviirako omuntu okuzitoowererwa, okufuna amazzi mangi, n'okufuna endwadde ey'ensiri.
Obulwadde bw'omulembe I n'ogw'omubiri II buviirako omuwendo gw'omubiri okugwa n'obutonde okuyongera amaanyi, ne kiba nti omuwendo gw'omubiri guba gutandise okukendeera era ne kiviirako omuwendo gw'omubiri okugwa.
N'olwekyo, okukebera mu kifuba okw'akabi ennyo, emirundi mingi kubaawo nga n'obulwadde obwo bukyali bwa maanyi.
