N'olwekyo, obuyambi mu kussa bukulu nnyo okuwonya obubonero n'okuwonya obulamu; nga buno buzingiramu obujjanjabi bwa oxygen obulamba, obujjanjabi bwa oxygen obuyitiridde, okufuuyira empewo okutali kwa bulabe era n'okufuuyira empewo okutali kwa bulabe okusinziira ku bunene bw'obulwadde.
Abalwadde abalina obubonero obw'amaanyi obw'okuwummulamu balina okuweebwa okusaasaanya omukka gwa oxygen (EMOC), enkola ey'okuzzaawo omutima oguyitibwa cardiopulmonary bypass ekozesebwa okujjanjaba obulwadde obw'omutima oba obw'okuwummulamu.
Okugatta ku ekyo, okukuuma obuwumbi bw'amasannyalaze, okutangira n'okujjanjaba endwadde ez'ekika ekya bbiri n'okusaasaana kw'omusujja, n'okukuuma ebitundu eby'omubiri ebikulu nabyo bikulu nnyo eri abalwadde abalina SARS-CoV-2.
Kimanyiddwa nti obulwadde bw'omubiri obuyitibwa SARS ne MERS buvaamu obulwadde bw'omubiri obuyitibwa cytokine shock.
Okwewuunya kwa cytokine ngeri ya kuddamu okw'obulumi obuli mu mubiri, nga kuzingiramu okufulumya cytokines ezitali zimu, omuli TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ ne MCP-1.
Zino cytokines ziviirako obutoffaali bw'omubiri okwekutula ku bulwadde okufulumya ebitundu ebingi eby'omubiri ebiyitibwa free radicals, nga bino bye bisinga okuviirako obulwadde bwa ARDS n'okulemererwa kw'ebitundu by'omubiri ebirala.
Okuziyiza obulwadde bw'omubiri kikulu nnyo mu kujjanjaba obulwadde bwa cytokine, naddala mu mbeera enzibu.
Corticosteroids ne tocilizumab, ekirwanyisa ekirwanyisa IL6 ekikola ku mubiri gumu, bikozesebwa okujjanjaba obulwadde bwa cytokine.
Okujjanjaba okulala okw'okulwanyisa obulwadde obuyitibwa cytokine kuzingiramu okukyusa obusobozi bw'omubiri obw'okwerinda nga bakozesa obutoffaali bwa T, okuziyiza cytokines IFN-γ, IL-1, ne TNF, okuziyiza JAK, blinatumomab, cytokine 4 signaling suppressor, n'okuziyiza HDAC.
Steroids, ng'ebirungo ebikugira obulwadde, bikozesebwa nnyo mu bujjanjabi bwa SARS okukendeeza ku buzibu bw'obulwadde.
Kyokka, okukozesa eddagala erikola eddagala eriyitibwa steroids mu bungi tekyavaamu kalungi konna ku bulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'amawuggwe mu balwadde ba SARS ne COVID-19.
Wabula, biyinza okuvaamu obuzibu obw'amaanyi, omuli n'obulwadde bwa ssukaali, ne bikola kinene ku mbeera y'omulwadde.
Wadde kiri kityo, okukozesa obwegendereza eddagala eritali lya maanyi eriyitibwa corticosteroids, kyasiimibwa nnyo eri abalwadde abalina obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Mu kiseera kino eky'okuwandiika, tewali ddagala liyinza kuyamba ku bulwadde buno.
Kyokka, okugaba remdesivir mu musaayi, eddagala eriyitibwa nucleoside analogue, kyalaga nti kya muganyulo mu mulwadde wa Amerika alina COVID-19.
Remdesivir ddagala eriggya erirwanyisa akawuka eryavaako akawuka ka siriimu eryavaako akawuka ka Ebola ne Marburg.
Oluvannyuma, remdesivir era yalaga nti esobola okulemesa obuwuka obulala obuli ku RNA, omuli MERS ne SARS.
Olw'ebyo ebyazuulibwa, Gilead yatuma ekirungo kino mu China okusobola okugezesa abantu abalina akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2, era ebivuddemu byasuubirwa nnyo.
Ate era, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir awamu ne ribavirin byalagiddwa ng'obujjanjabi obuyinza okuweebwa abalwadde abalina obubonero obw'okuwummulamu obw'amaanyi.
Obulwadde bw'omukaba, okulumwa, okuluka, obuzibu mu kibumba n'ebirala biyinza okubaawo oluvannyuma lw'okufuna eddagala eriyitibwa lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Enkolagana y'eddagala lino n'eddagala eddala eryakozesebwa mu balwadde eryo erina okwekeberebwa ennyo.
Plasma y'abalwadde abawonye era n'okufulumya obuwuka obutta obulwadde
Okukuŋŋaanya omusaayi okuva mu balwadde abawonye obulwadde obw'akabi okujjanjaba abalwadde abalala abalina obulwadde obwo oba okukuuma abantu abalamu obulungi okuva ku bulwadde obwo, kikolwa kya dda nnyo.
Abantu abawona batera okuba n'omulwadde ow'amaanyi.
Antibodies ye immunoglobulin (Ig) ekolebwa B lymphocytes okulwanyisa endwadde n'ebirala ebitalina kye bikolawo; zimanya obuwuka obuli mu ndwadde ne buzibulako butereevu.
Mu ngeri eyo, plasma yaggibwa mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abaawonyezebwa COVID-19 ne giweebwa abalwadde 10 abaali balwadde ennyo.
Obubonero bwabwe bwagenda bukyuka mu ssaawa 24, nga bukwataganyizibwa n'okukendeera mu bulumi, okukendeera mu bungi bw'akawuka, n'okweyongera kw'omukka oguyitibwa oxygen mu musaayi.
Kyokka, okukakasa n'okutangaaza byetaagisa okusobola okuwa amagezi ku nkola eno okukozesebwa ku kigero ekinene okutuusa ng'obujjanjabi obw'enjawulo tebunnakolebwa.
Ate era, olw'obujjanjabi, ebizibu ebimu ebiva mu kukozesa plasma bisaanidde okwekenneenyezebwa.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuwuka obuziyiza obulwadde busobola okuleetera omuntu okwekutula ku bulwadde n'okuvaamu obulwadde obuyitibwa cytokine syndrome.
Obusobozi bw'omubiri okuziyiza obulwadde mu musaayi butera okuba obutonotono, era obwetaavu bwa plasma okujjanjaba abalwadde abalwadde ennyo bwa maanyi.
Kizibu okuteekawo n'okufulumya eddagala erigema obulwadde buno amangu ddala okusobola okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino.
N'olwekyo, kikulu nnyo era kya muganyulo nnyo okwawula obutoffaali bwa B okuva mu balwadde abawonye era n'okumanya obubonero bw'ekika obuwa obuwuka obubakwatako oba okunoonya obuwuka obuziyiza obutoffaali obukulu obuli mu kawuka.
Kino kyandireetedde abantu okwongera ku bungi bw'omubiri oguyitibwa antibody.
TCM ekozesebwa okumala enkumi n'enkumi z'emyaka mu China okujjanjaba endwadde ez'enjawulo.
Kyokka, ebikolwa byago bisinziira nnyo ku kugatta awamu ebintu bingi mu ngeri eyeeyawukana okusinziira ku ngeri omuntu gy'alagamu obulwadde obwo.
Ebintu ebisinga ebiyamba mu kujjanjaba endwadde tebimanyiddwa nnyo oba tebimanyiddwa n'akamu kubanga kizibu okubiggyamu n'okubikebera oba okumanya enkola ennungi ey'okubikozesa.
Mu kiseera kino, olw'obutaba na bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19 obwa namaddala, TCM y'emu ku bujjanjabi obusinga okuweebwa abalwadde abalina obubonero obutonotono oba obw'amaanyi oba obulwadde obuba buzzeemu.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, eddagala eriyitibwa Shu Feng Jie Du ne Lian Hua Qing Wen lilabise nga ddungi nnyo mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Ebisale ebisinga obulungi eby'okuwona COVID-19 byalabikira mu ssaza lya China eriko abantu 87 ku buli kikumi abakozesa TCM, omuli Gansu (63.7 ku buli kikumi), Ningxia (50 ku buli kikumi) ne Hunan (50 ku buli kikumi), ate ssaza lya Hubei eririna abantu 30 ku buli kikumi abakozesa TCM ku balwadde ba COVID-19 lye lisinga okuba wansi (13 ku buli kikumi).
Kyokka, kino kikwatagana butereevu kubanga waliwo ebintu ebirala bingi ebirina akakwate, gamba ng'omuwendo gw'abalwadde n'obulwadde, ebirina okwetegerezebwa mu kunoonyereza.
Nga Febwali 18, 2020, Boli Zhang ne banne baafulumya okunoonyereza okwageraageranya obujjanjabi obw'ebika eby'ebitundu eby'ebuvanjuba (MO) n'obujjanjabi obwakozesebwa mu kugatta MD ne TCM.
Kyakakasibwa nti ekiseera eky'okudda ku mubiri okubuguma, ekiseera eky'okuggyawo obubonero, n'ekiseera eky'okusibibwa mu ddwaliro byali bya buseera mu kibiina kya MO+MTC okusinga mu kibiina kya MO kyokka.
Ekisingawo n'okusikiriza, omuwendo gw'obulwadde (okuva ku mutono okutuuka ku munene) gwali mutono nnyo mu kibiina kya MO+MTC okusinga mu kibiina kya MO kyokka (7.4% ku 46.2%) era okufa kwali kutono mu kibiina kya MO+MTC okusinga mu kibiina kya MO kyokka (8.8% ku 39%).
Kyokka, obutuufu n'obutebenkevu bwa TCM bikyaliwo okutegeerekeka okuyita mu kugezesebwa okufuga okukolebwa ku kigero ekisingawo era mu bifo ebisingawo.
Era kyandibadde kya muganyulo okunnyonnyola engeri gye kikolebwamu n'okulaga ebizingirwa mu bujjanjabi bwa TCM oba obugatta ku bujjanjabi obwo, bwe kiba kisoboka.
Abantu abazuulibwa ng'abayinza okuba nga balina COVID-19 oba abaakakasibwa nti balina obulwadde buno batera okweraliikirira ennyo obulwadde buno obuyitibwa COVID-19 era obufa, ate n'abo ababeera mu kifo ekyesudde nabo bafuna ensonyi, ekiwuubaalo n'obusungu.
Okugatta ku ekyo, obubonero bw'obulwadde, gamba ng'omusujja, okukaaba, n'okukoowa, awamu n'ebizibu ebiva mu bujjanjabi, gamba ng'okuloota olw'omusaayi, biyinza okuleetera omuntu okweraliikirira ennyo n'okweraliikirira.
Mu kiseera kya SARS, obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'ebirowoozo bungi bwazuulibwa, omuli obwennyamivu obutaggwaawo, okweraliikirira, okutya, okweraliikirira, obubonero bw'obulwadde obw'obwongo, okutabuka ennyo, n'okwegomba okwetta.
Okunoonya abantu n'okubateeka mu ddwaaliro ng'ekitundu ky'ebyobulamu mu kulwanyisa COVID-19 kiyinza okwongera ku kweraliikirira n'okulumiriza abalwadde ku bizibu ebiva mu kuyingira, okubategekera, n'okulumya ab'eŋŋanda zaabwe ne mikwano gyabwe.
N'olwekyo, obujjanjabi bw'ebirowoozo bulina okuweebwa abalwadde abalina COVID-19, abantu abalabiddwa ng'abayinza okuba abalwadde, abantu abakwatagana n'abantu abo, n'abantu abalala abali mu buzibu.
Obuyambi buno obw'eby'omwoyo bulina okuzingiramu okutendeka ebibinja eby'enjawulo, empuliziganya ennungi n'okutegeeza obutayosa ebikwata ku kawumpuli wa SARS-CoV-2 n'enteekateeka z'obujjanjabi, n'okukozesa programu n'ebikozesebwa eby'amasannyalaze eby'enjawulo okwewala okukwatagana.
Ensigo ez'omugaso nkulu nnyo mu kuggyawo obuwuka okuva mu nsolo n'abantu abalina obulwadde okudda mu bantu abalina obulwadde, era zitera okuwewula ku ddagala erirwanyisa akawuka mu kufuga obulwadde obuva mu bika bya kawuka.
Kaweefube akoleddwa okuzimba eddagala eririna protein S, okufulumya ebirwanyisa omubiri ebiruma omubiri okumala ebbanga era/oba okuleeta obutebenkevu obukuuma ku SARS-CoV.
Ensigo eziriwo ezirwadde SARS ezirongooseddwa zaakeberebwa mu nsolo.
Kyokka, obumanyirivu mu bantu abakaddiye n'obw'okulwanyisa obulwadde obuviirako okufa n'obukuumi ku bulwadde bwa virus ez'ekisolo, tebinnategeerekeka kubanga tewali kigezo ky'ekinnansi ekyatandikibwawo.
Kino kirabika kiva ku kuba nti SARS yaggwaawo emyaka 17 egiyise era tewali mulwadde mulala yenna eyazuulibwa okuva olwo.
Kyokka, obulwadde bwa MERS obutali bumu n'ebifo mwe buva bikyaliwo mu Buvanjuba bwa Buvanjuba n'ebitundu ebirala olw'ebitundu omuli endwadde eziri mu nsolo.
Enkola ez'enjawulo ez'okulwanyisa MERS ezikozesebwa mu kukozesa akawuka, DNA plasmids, ebirwadde, nanoparticles, ebitundu eby'omusaayi n'ebitundu by'amagi agazze gakwatagana, zeezze zitandikibwawo era ezimu ku zo zikozesebwa mu bisolo.
Okukulaakulanya eddagala eryesigika era ery'omugaso eri SARS-CoV-2 eri abantu abatalina bulwadde buno kye kintu ekikulu ennyo ekirina okukolebwa mu bwangu okusobola okufuga ekirwadde kino.
Kyokka, kino kizibu nnyo olw'ekiseera ekiwanvu (emyezi 18 ku buli kikumi) ekyetaagisa okuzimba eddagala n'enkulaakulana y'obulwadde bwa coronavirus.
Olw'okuba obulwadde buno bujjawo, COVID-19 kati etandise okukulaakulana mu ddwaaliro ng'eyisa enkumi n'enkumi z'abalwadde.
Emirundi egisinga obungi abalwadde bawona mpolampola nga tewali kizibu kyonna kibaluseeko.
Kyokka, okufaananako SARS ne MERS, COVID-19 era erina akakwate n'obulwadde n'okufa okw'amaanyi mu balwadde abakulu.
N'olwekyo, okuteekawo enkola y'okulangirira obulwadde kikulu nnyo eri ebitongole by'ebyobulamu okusobola okukulembeza obuweereza bwabwe, naddala mu bitundu ebirimu eby'obugagga ebitono.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa, ebintu ebiyinza okukwata oba okukwatagana n'okusaasaanya obulwadde bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 bye bino wammanga (Lupapula (Lupapula33)):
Emyaka: Emyaka kye kintu ekisinga okuleetera omuntu okuzuula obulwadde bwa SARS, era kirabika bwe kiri ne ku COVID-19.
COVID-19 esinga kukosa abantu abali wakati w'emyaka 30 ne 65, nga 47,7% ku bo basukka mu myaka 50 okusinziira ku kunoonyereza okwakolebwa ku bantu 8,866, nga bwe kiragiddwa waggulu.
Abalwadde abaalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi baali basobola okufuna obulwadde obulala n'ebizibu, era baali bakulu nnyo (emyaka 66 ng'oggyeko 51,), ekiraga nti emyaka gy'omuntu kye kiviirako obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Ekika: SARS-CoV-2 yafuna abalenzi bangi okusinga abakazi (0.31/100,000 ng'oggyeko 0.27/100,000), nga bwe kyayogerwako waggulu.
Obulwadde n'ebizibu: abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga okulabirirwa mu ddwaliro eriyamba ennyo basinga kufuna ebisago eby'omutima n'okubula.
Ebintu eby'omutima nabyo bye byaviirako abantu okufa ennyo olw'obulwadde bwa SARS.
Kimanyiddwa nti SARS-CoV-2 era esobola okukwata ku cholangiocytes eza ACE2 eziyinza okuviirako obulwadde bw'ekibumba mu balwadde ba COVID-19.
Kikulu okukijjukira nti emyaka n'okuba n'obulwadde obuli wansi waago bikwatagana era bisobola okutabangula.
Ebiva mu bigezo: omuwendo gwa C-reactive protein (CRP) mu musaayi gukakasa obulumi oba obuvune obuli mu bitundu by'omubiri; era gwabadde gutegeeza obulwadde, obujjanjabi n'okuwona.
Enkolagana wakati w'omuwendo gwa CRP n'obuzibu n'okulaga nti omuntu anaatera okufuna COVID-19 nayo eyogerwako.
Ate era, omuwendo omunene ogw'ekika kya lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), daspartate aminotransferase (AST), dalanine aminotransferase (ALT), ne creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bisobola okuyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde.
Enzime zino zinyumirwa nnyo mu bitundu by'omubiri ebitali bimu, gamba ng'omutima n'ekibumba, era zifuluma bwe wabaawo obuzibu mu bitundu by'omubiri.
N'olwekyo, ebitundu bino by'omubiri bikwataganyizibwa n'obulwadde bw'omutima oba obw'ekibumba.
Obubonero obukulu: Ebiva mu bifaananyi by'omutima n'ebiseera eby'obubonero obwenjawulo birina okwekenneenyezebwa awamu n'ebintu ebirala okusobola okumanya obulwadde bw'ekika kya COVID-19 n'ebizibu ebivaamu.
Okukozesa steroids: Nga bwe kyogeddwako waggulu, steroids ziyamba mu kulwanyisa obulwadde obuyitibwa immunosuppressants era zitera kukozesebwa ng'eddagala eryongera ku bulwadde obuyitibwa infectious disease okugabanya obulwadde obuyitibwa inflammatory lesions.
Olw'okuba eddagala eriyitibwa corticosteroids ery'ekigero ekya waggulu lyeyongera okukozesebwa ku bantu abalina obulwadde bwa SARS obw'amaanyi, bangi ku abo abaawonawo baafuna obulwadde bwa bufuba obuva ku musaayi ogutakola bulungi era ne bafiirwa obulamu bwabwe.
N'olwekyo, bwe kiba kyetaagisa, okuwa abalwadde abalina COVID-19 eddagala eriyitibwa steroids kulina kuba kutono era ku bbanga ttono.
Okweraliikirira okw'omunda: Nga bwe kyayogeddwako waggulu, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kivuddemu abantu bangi abalina okweraliikirira okw'amaanyi, abalwadde batera okubeera mu kifo ekyesudde okumala ekiseera kiwanvu, obutebenkevu obw'amaanyi, n'okufa kw'abaagalwa baabwe oba abalwadde abalala.
Kikulu nnyo okuwa abantu abo obuyambi obw'ebiseera eby'omu maaso okusobola okubayamba okuvvuunuka ebizibu ebyo n'okuddamu okuba abalamu obulungi.
Okusinziira ku kunoonyereza ku bantu okwakolebwa okutuusa kati, COVID-19 erabika ng'erina endwadde ez'enjawulo ku SARS.
Ng'oggyeko okuzaala mu mputtu z'omukka ez'oku nsi, SARS-CoV-2 era ezzaala bulungi mu mputtu z'omukka ez'oku waggulu era tezivaamu bubonero bwonna oba butono nnyo mu kiseera eky'olubuto, nga bwe kiri ku korona obwaviirako ekirwadde kya ssennyiga.
N'olwekyo, abantu abaakafuna obulwadde oba abali mu kiseera eky'okwekweka basobola okufulumya obuwumbi bwa kawuka mu mirimu gyabwe egy'ennaku zonna, ekireetera obuzibu okufuga ekirwadde.
Kyokka, SARS-CoV yatwalibwanga nti eyambulwa abalwadde abalwadde ennyo, nga n'obuzibu bw'okusasaanya mu kitundu ekisooka butono nnyo.
N'olwekyo, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekiriko kati kya maanyi nnyo era kizibu okufuga okusinga SARS.
Kaakano waliwo okufuba okw'amaanyi mu China, nga muno mwe muli okugoba Wuhan n'ebibuga ebiriraanyeewo, n'okusiba abantu kumpi bonna mu kifo ekyesudde okusobola okukomya okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2.
Wadde ng'enteekateeka zino zirina kinene kye zikoze ku by'enfuna wamu n'ebitundu ebirala mu ggwanga, omuwendo gw'abalwadde abapya gukendeera, ekiraga nti obulwadde bukendedde.
Ebiteberezebwa nti obulwadde buno bujja kukoma mu March era nti ekiseera eky'okudduka kijja kumala emyezi esatu oba ena.
Kyokka, si bakugu bonna abali mu nsi eyo nti balina essuubi eryo.
