Ng'ekyokulabirako, ORF4 yonna eyabula mu HCoV-229E ey'olubereberye, olw'okuvvuunuka obuwuka bubiri.
Wadde nga ORF4 yali esobola okulabikira mu bulwadde bwa HCoV-229E obuli mu bulwadde bwa balongo n'obwa ŋŋamira, alpaca alpha-CoV erina obuwuka obuli mu bulwadde obwo obuyingiza obuwuka obw'omulembe, ne kiviirako obuwuka obwo okuggwamu amaanyi.
Mu ngeri y'emu, waliwo abantu abawerako abaafa olw'obulwadde bwa HCoVs.
Abantu abatalina bubonero oba abaalina obubonero obutonotono balabiddwa ng'enkoko zirwadde CoVs, ekiraga nti CoVs n'enkoko zaakolebwako.
Kirabika nti abalongo beeyisa bulungi ku CoVs mu ngeri y'omubiri n'obutonde.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuzibu mu kukubiriza obuwuka obuviirako obulwadde mu nkoko bukendeeza ku bulwadde obuva ku CoV.
Ate era, ebitundu by'omubiri eby'ekika kya ssenyiga omukambwe mu mbuzi biziyizibwa olw'okufuga obulungi ekikwatirwa ekika kya ssenyiga omukambwe ekya NKG2/CD94 era n'olw'okuba nti obusobozi bw'okukozesa obusirikitu bwa ttendekero lya ssenyiga omukadde ery'okufaanana mu kibinja I bwa wansi.
Ate era, omuwendo omunene ogw'ebirungo bya oxygen ebikolera ku bintu ebiva mu by'omubiri eby'ekika kino kiyinza okulemesa CoV okuzaala era n'okukosa ekika ekyo ekikola ku by'omubiri, ekireetawo obuzibu obw'amaanyi n'okuvaamu obuwuka obuleeta endwadde bwe bufuluma mu muntu omulala.
Embeera z'akawuka ka CoV ezisingawo okuba n'obulwadde nazo zisobola okukyuka nga zikwatagana, ne zivaamu obutooke obupya oba engeri z'obutooke ez'okutuukana n'omulabe.
N'olwekyo, tekiri kya butanwa nti HCoVs ssatu empya zaabaddewo mu myaka 20 egiyise.
CoV si za bulwadde oba zireeta bubonero obutonotono mu bantu abazirimu gamba ng'ebisolo n'eŋŋamira.
Zino ze zikola enkulaakulana ey'amaanyi nga teziviiriddeko muntu kufuna bulwadde.
Kino kye kyama ky'okumanya abajjanjabi abatalina bubonero n'ekireeta obulwadde obw'amaanyi mu bantu.
Obubonero obw'amaanyi businga kuva ku buzibu bw'omubiri n'okulumwa kw'omubiri; obusobozi bw'omubiri bwe businga okuba obw'amaanyi, n'omutima gwe gusinga okwonooneka.
Okwawukana ku ekyo, mu abo abatalina bubonero, obulwadde buno tebwava ku CoV.
Enkola y'emu ey'okuggya obulwadde ku mubiri esobola okubaamu emiganyulo mu bujjanjabi bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okuddamu kwa interferon kwa maanyi nnyo mu nkima.
N'olwekyo, okugaba interferon eya kika I waakiri mu kiseera eky'olubereberye eky'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 kisuubirwa okuba eky'omuganyulo.
Ate era, okulongoosa mu bulwadde bwa NLRP3 tekuli bulungi mu mpiso.
Nga tugoberera endowooza eno, okuziyiza NLRP3 ne MCC950 kiyinza okuba eky'omuganyulo mu bujjanjabi bwa COVID-19.
SARS-CoV-2 yajja ng'egoberera enkola eya SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV.
Wadde nga beta-CoV eya kalangala eyafuna ebitundu 95 ku buli kikumi eby'obumu bwa nucleotide ne SARS-CoV yazuulibwa, waliwo ne CoV eya kalangala eyafuna ebitundu 96 ku buli kikumi eby'obumu bwa nucleotide ne SARS-CoV-2.
Wadde nga ebinyonyi eby'omu nsiko n'ebisolo ebirala ebiri mu butale byazuulibwa nga birina akawuka akafaanana n'aka SARS-CoV, tewali muntu yenna eyali mu kifo ekimu ne SARS-CoV-2 eyali amanyiddwa.
Beta-CoV z'ekitooke eziri mu ngeri y'emu ne SARS-CoV-2 zaalabikira, nga biraga nti ekitooke kiyinza okuba ekimu ku bisenge ebirimu oba nti beta-CoV y'ekitooke esobola okuteekawo ebitundu by'ekitooke eby'enkula ya SARS-CoV-2.
Wadde ng'ebibuuzo bikyaliwo, tewali bukakafu bulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yakolebwa bantu, ka kibe nga kyakolebwa mu bugenderevu oba mu butanwa.
CoV zikomyewo mu bantu olw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okunoonyereza ku CoV mu nkima n'ensolo endala kikyusizza nnyo endowooza yaffe ku kifo eky'ensolo n'ebisolo mu kusindika HCoV mu bantu.
Waliwo obukakafu bungi obulaga nti SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, ne SARS-CoV-2 byava mu nkoko era ne bisasaana ku bantu okuyitira mu bantu abalala.
Olw'okuba obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV buva ku bantu okukwatagana n'ebinyonyi ebiri mu butale, okuggyawo obutale bw'ebyamaguzi n'okutta ebinyonyi ebyali mu butale obwo kyandisobozesezza okukomya ekirwadde kya SARS.
Mu ngeri y'emu, ensolo ez'omu nsiko zirina okuggibwa mu butale bw'ebyamaguzi ebiggya okwewala endwadde z'ensolo, olw'okuba waliwo ensolo nnyingi ez'omu nsiko ezirina enkola ya beta-CoV ezikwatagana ne SARS-CoV-2.
Kyokka, oba nga SARS-CoV-2 ekwatulwa okuva ku mpologoma n'ebisolo ebirala eri abantu, era bwe kiba kityo, engeri ekwatulwa gye kibaawo, kijja kuddamu okuzuulibwa mu kunoonyereza okujja.
Ku luuyi olulala, MERS-CoV emaze ebbanga ddene mu mpologoma.
Eŋŋamira ezo zaali za mugaso nnyo mu by'entambula era nga ze zaali zisinga okufunamu ennyama, amata, amasavu, n'ebyoya by'ebisibo.
Babeera mu bitundu bya Buwalabu ne Afirika.
N'olwekyo, tekisoboka kutta ŋŋamira zonna okuziyiza MERS, nga bwe kyakolebwa mu butale bw'ensolo ez'omu nsiko mu China okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okumalawo obulwadde bwa MERS obuzze bucaaka, enkola yonna esaanidde okukolebwa okuzuula eddagala erigasa erirwanyisa MERS-CoV mu ŋŋamira, nga lirina n'enteekateeka endala ez'okuziyiza obulwadde.
Olw'okuba tetusobola kumalawo bulwadde buno, genotypes empya zisobola okujja ne ziviirako obulwadde.
Waliwo CoV ez'enjawulo ez'ekisolo eziyita mu butonde.
Naddala CoV z'ensiri, ezirina obusobozi bw'okutta abantu.
Waliwo omukisa gwonna nti CoV eziri mu nsolo ziyinza okukyuka era ne zikwatagana, ne kiviirako CoV empya okulabika ez'obutwa n'okutta abantu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Enkola y'okulya ensolo enkambwe mu bitundu ebimu ebya China erina okuggibwawo okukendeeza ku kukwatagana okw'obuteetaagisa wakati w'abantu n'ensolo.
Nga twolekaganye n'ebizibu ebiva mu SARS, MERS ne COVID-19, twetaaga enteekateeka ennungi ey'okwetegekera n'okuddamu.
Mu butuufu, waliwo obuwuka bungi obumaze ebbanga eddene ku nsi.
Basigala mu bifo byabwe eby'obutonde okutuusa lwe wabaawo akakisa okusaasaanya obulwadde.
Wadde ng'endwadde z'ensiri zirina engeri nnyingi ezireetera abantu okuzaala obulwadde, abantu bwe bayigirizibwa okwewala endwadde, basobola okukendeeza ku busobozi bwabwe obw'okufuna endwadde.
Okulabirira ensolo ezisaala okw'omuddiriŋŋanwa kyetaagisa okusobola okutegeera obulungi ekikula ky'abantu abafaako n'ekika kyazo, ekinaayamba mu kuziyiza okusaasaanyizibwa kw'ensolo eri abantu n'obulwadde obw'omu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Mu nkomerero, engeri esingayo obulungi abantu okuziyiza endwadde z'ebisolo kwe kwewala ebitundu eby'obutonde eby'ebitundu eby'obutonde eby'endwadde z'ebisolo.
Ebyama byonna ebikwata ku nsibuko ya SARS-CoV-2 okuva mu nsolo tebinnategeerekeka.
Okusooka, singa abalongo basindika akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 eri abalongo, kyandibadde kirungi okwetegereza embeera abalongo n'abalongo mwe bayinza okubeera mu kifo kye kimu.
Ekyokubiri, singa abalongo balina ekifo ekisingawo mu kuyingiza obulwadde mu bantu, abantu balina okumanya engeri gye bayita mu bulwadde buno.
Ekyokusatu, singa waliwo ensolo endala ey'omu nsiko ekola ng'ey'omuwendo, tekinnaba kutegeerekeka ngeri gye yeeyisaamu n'ebika ebirala, omuli abantu, abalongo, n'ebisolo ebiyitibwa pangolins.
N'ekisembayo, olw'okuba ebisolo bingi, naddala ebisolo eby'awaka, biyinza okufuna SARS-CoV-2, kyetaagisa okulondoola n'okugezaako okubikosa.
Ka kibe nti sseseŋŋendo, pangolin, oba ensolo endala, SARS-CoV-2 oba obuwuka bwa bazadde obwenkanankana ennyo obuli mu bantu ababubeeramu buyinza okuzuulibwa.
Okunoonyereza okunaatera okubaawo mu kitundu kino kujja kuyamba okutegeera engeri SARS-CoV-2 gye yeeyisaamu mu bisolo era kujja kubaako kye kukola ku kukuuma n'okufuga COVID-19 mu bantu.
Kikulu okuzza obuggya ebisaanyizo by'okunoonyereza ku  abantu abateeberezebwa  n'abo  abakakasibwa  COVID-19
Nga Febwali 6, 2020, ttiimu yaffe yafulumya Ekiragiro eky'Amangu eky'Okubuulirira ku Kulaba n'Okujjanjaba akawuka ka Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) era ekiragiro kino kyalaga obumanyirivu bwaffe era ne kiwa obulagirizi ku kulwanyisa kawumpuli ono okwetooloola ensi yonna.
Kyokka, obulwadde bwa coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) bukyali bwa mulembe, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kwe tulina kweyongera mpolampola okusinziira ku ebyo ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'okumanya okuva mu nkola y'ekisawo; n'olwekyo, enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Mu bbaluwa eno, twaddamu ekyebuuzibwa ku bulagirizi bwaffe era ne tuwaayo ebisaanyizo eby'okunoonyereza eby'omulembe ku  omuntu gwe bateebereza  n'omuntu gwe bategeerekeseeko  okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwa COVID-19 obw'okunoonyereza n'obujjanjabi (obw'omusanvu) obwasindikibwa National Health Commission of the People's Republic of China.
Mu Ddesemba 2019, akawuka ka coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) kaaleetawo ekivundu kati ekimanyiddwa nga coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), era akawuka kaayitibwa coronavirus severe acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga 11 Maaki 2020, WHO yatandikawo COVID-19 ng'ekirwadde ekirwadde.
Okusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yakola amagezi amangu agaafulumizibwa ku mukutu gwa Intaneeti mu Military Medical Research nga Febwali 6, 2020.
Ekitabo kino kivudde ku mulembe nga kitongozebwa.
Kyokka, tukwegayiridde weetegereze nti COVID-19 ndwadde empya, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kwe tulina kweyongera mpolampola okusinziira ku ebyo ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'okwolesebwa kw'ekikyala; n'olwekyo enkola z'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba nazo zikyusibwa buli kiseera.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obulagirizi obukwata ku kuzuula n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 obwakubibwa National Health Commission of the People's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) bwafulumizibwa emirundi musanvu wakati wa Jjanwali 16, 2020 ne Maaki 3, 2020, era ebimu ku byo byaliko enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi.
Ekiragiro kyaffe bwe kyaweebwa Zhou et al., baatuwa amagezi ag'okugezesa mu ngeri ennyangu okusinziira ku bumanyirivu bwabwe.
Omulimu gwabwe guleetedde obujulizi obupya ku bulagirizi bwaffe era era guli mukisa gwa muwendo mu kulwanyisa kawumpuli ono ow'ensi yonna.
Tukkiriziganya n'omulimu gwabwe omukulu era tubeebaza.
Kyokka, omulimu gwabwe gwetaaga okuvuganyisibwa okusinziira ku bulagirizi obwakasembayo obw'okunoonyereza n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 (okugezesebwa okw'omusanvu) n'okunoonyereza okwaliwo mu kiseera kino.
Okusinziira ku kivvulu ky'omusanvu (Makozi 3, 2020), okukakasa omuntu eyeekweka kulina okukwataganya ekimu ku bintu ebiri mu byafaayo by'ekirwadde n'ebirala bibiri eby'obulwadde okusobola okukola okunoonyereza okujjuvu, oba kulina okukwatagana n'ebirala bisatu eby'obulwadde nga tewali bulwadde obumanyiddwa obulungi:
Ebyafaayo by'obulwadde: (1) eby'okuyitawo oba okubeera mu kibuga Wuhan n'ebitundu ebiriraanyewo oba mu bitundu ebirala omwabadde abantu abalina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ez'oluvannyuma ng'obubonero tebunnaba kulabika; (2) eby'okubeera n'abantu abalina obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 (nga bakeberebwa ne balaba nti balina obuwuka bwa nucleic acid); (3) eby'okubeera n'abalwadde abalina omusujja oba obubonero bw'omukka okuva mu kibuga Wuhan oba mu bitundu ebiriraanyewo oba mu bitundu ebirala omwabadde abantu abalina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ez'oluvannyuma ng'obubonero tebunnaba kulabika; (4) eby'okubeera n'abantu abawerako (nga balina omusujja n'obubonero bw'omukka mu wiiki 2 oba n'okusingawo mu ssomero, mu ofiisi, mu maka, n'ebirala).
Ebintu eby'ekisawo: (1) omusujja n'obubonero bw'okuwummulamu; (2) ebifaananyi ebiraga obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19; (3) omuwendo gw'ensolo enjeru ez'omusaayi ezibala omuwendo gwa ssekinnoomu, ogukendeera oba ogukendeera ng'obubonero butandise.
Okuzuula omuntu alina obulwadde obukakafu kulina kwesigamizibwa ku muntu gwe balowooza nti alina obulwadde oba obujulizi bwonna obuli mu SARS-CoV-2: (1) okugezesebwa kwa PCR mu kiseera ekituufu nga bujjudde SARS-CoV-2; (2) okukebera mu ngeri y'omutindo gwa virus yonna nga bw'egatta n'obulwadde bwa coronavirus obupya obuli mu nsi; (3) okukebera kwa SARS-CoV-2 IgM ne IgG antibody nga bujjudde; oba okukyusa antibody ya SARS-CoV-2 eya IgG okuva ku negative okudda ku positive oba okwongera ku bungi bwayo emirundi ≥ 4 mu kiseera ky'okuwona okuva ku kiseera eky'obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Tusobola okulaba nti okugezesa kwa PCR okw'ekiseera ekituufu okw'amasannyalaze mu mpeke oba mu musaayi gw'omuntu kyongeddwa mu kivvulu eky'okubiri (Jjanwali 18, 2020) ne mu kivvulu eky'okusatu (Jjanwali 22, 2020).
Okukebera obulwadde okuva mu musaayi gw'omuntu kyayongerwako mu kivvulu eky'okuna (Jjanwali 27, 2020) ne mu kyaokutaano (February 8, 2020); oluvannyuma obujulizi bw'omusaayi bwayongerwako mu kivvulu eky'omusanvu.
Enkyukakyuka zino zinyweza omulimu ogukyagenda mu maaso ogw'abanoonyereza okufuna ekikozesebwa ekisinga obulungi mu kunoonyereza ku bulwadde bwa nucleic acid okusobola okunoonyereza amangu, wamu n'ebitundu by'omukka ogw'oku mufuufu omuli n'okukuba omusaayi, nga waliwo ebitundu bingi, era byayamba mu kwongera ku mulundi ogumu ogwazuuliddwa omubiri ogumu mu bipimo ebyakakasibwa.
Ate era, obujulizi bweyongera okutujjukiza okwegendereza abalwadde abalina obubonero obutali bumu n'abo abatalina bubonero.
N'olwekyo, ekifaananyi kya Zhou et al. kyetaaga okuddaabirizibwa kubanga baakuteeka abantu abatalina bubonero bwa bulwadde mu mbeera ya 'low risk'.
Enkola y'okugezesa nayo erina okukakasibwa mu nkola y'ekisawo n'ebyenjigiriza eby'omu maaso.
Mu nkomerero, tusuubira obujulizi obwennyini okujjawo era tusaba abasomi okuteekawo endowooza zaabwe.
Ku bikwata ku kunoonyereza ku  abalwadde abateeberezebwa  n'abo  abakakasibwa , tubalagira okugoberera n'okukwata obulagirizi obuli mu nsi yaabwe.
Ekibinja kyaffe era kijja kuddamu okuteekateeka ekiragiro kyaffe mu kiseera ekituufu okubawa obuyambi.
Bangladesh etaddewo abantu bataano abafa COVID-19, akabonero ak'ennaku emu
Eggulo, Bangladesh yakakasa okufa kwa bantu abataano okuva ku COVID-19 mu lunaku lumu lwokka.
Kino kivuddeko ensi okuwandiika omuwendo omunene ennyo ogw'abantu abafa obulwadde buno mu lunaku lumu.
Eggulo, ekitongole kya Bangladesh Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) kyagamba nti abantu abaakafuna obulwadde buno baali 114 ate 33 bawonye era nga basibiddwa awaka.
Abantu 17 be baafa.
Okuggya entambula ya bonna kwatandika nga March 26 era kwateekeddwa okukoma ku Lwomukaaga, April 4.
