Ate era, waliwo abantu bangi abalina obulwadde bwa HCoVs.
Okukebera ebisolo birina kinene kye kikola mu kuziyiza endwadde z'abantu.
Okunoonyereza ku ngeri CoV gy'ekolagana n'omulabe mu nsolo nakyo kiyinza okuyamba mu kutegeera obulungi CoV mu bantu.
Okusinziira ku njawulo mu ngeri za protein, CoV zigabanyizibwamu mu bika bina (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, ne delta-CoV). Ekika kya Beta-CoV kirimu HCoV ezisinga obungi era kigabanyizibwamu mu bika bina (A, B, C, ne D).
Obujulizi bw'obutonde bulaze nti ebinyeebwa n'ebisenge bye bivaako alpha-CoVs n'ebitonde ebirala ebirina beta-CoVs, ate ebinyonyi bye bisinga okuteekawo gamma-CoVs ne delta-CoVs.
Okutuusa kati, waliwo abantu musanvu abalina akawuka ka HCoV.
Mu bano, HCoV-229E ne HCoV-NL63 ze alfa-CoV.
Beta-CoV endala etaano kuliko HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, Ssenyiga omukambwe (SARS-CoV), Ssenyiga ow'omu Buvanjuba (MERS-CoV), ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okuzuula ensibuko y'ekika kya HCoV kiwa enkola ey'okutegeera ebyafaayo by'ebika, ebikuleetera n'ebiremesa ebika okusomoka.
Era kiyinza okukulembera oba okuyambako mu kunoonya omulabirizi (s) omubeezi, omutabaganya, era omuwagizi wa SARS-CoV-2, nga kino kirina kinene kye kikola mu kuziyiza endwadde mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
CoV eziri mu bisolo zimanyiddwa okuva mu myaka gya 1930.
Mu myaka egiyise, HCoVs musanvu ze zaawera.
Ekika ekisooka ekya HCoV-229E kyasangibwa mu biwuka by'omukka mu balwadde abaalina ekirwadde ky'omu biwundu mu 1966, era oluvannyuma kyafuuka ekikula mu bitundu by'omukka eby'omu mawuggwe WI-38.
Abalwadde abalina akawuka ka HCoV-229E baayoleka obubonero bw'omukka omungi, nga mw'otwalidde omutwe, okusuubula, obulumi n'omumwa, nga n'omusujja n'okusula bibaawo mu bitundu 10 ku buli kikumi.
HCoV-229E ne HCoV-OC43 zombi ziri mu nsi yonna era kirabika zisasaana nnyo mu biseera by'obutiti, mu nsi ezirimu embeera y'obudde ey'ekikafu.
