Okusobola okukendeeza ku bbula ly'emmere, Coles yalagidde ebipimo ebinene okuva mu batunzi era n'ayongera ku bungi bw'ebitundutundu, Woolworths yalagidde ebirungo ebirala, ate ALDI yafulumya ebirungo ku makya olw'okusasulira ku Lwokusatu.
