Okunaaba mu mazzi ag'omukaaga kiyinza okuviirako engalo okuddamu okwonooneka.
Koola n'ettaala ennongoofu oba mu bbanga.
Ebikono ebinyevu n'ebinyevu biyinza okuggwamu obulwadde buno. Ebitundu ebitera okwerabirwa bye bigere, engalo, wakati w'engalo n'amannyo.
Enkolako y'enkwaso n'ebikoola by'enkwaso ebiba bifumitiddwa biyinza okubaamu obuwuka.
Okuteeka eddagala erikendeeza ku buwuka emirundi mingi kiyamba omuntu okwewala okugwa engalo; enkuba bw'eba enkalu, ekitundu ky'olususu kiba kivudde ku buwuka obuyinza okwongera ku kabi k'okusannyalala.
Waliwo enkola endala nnyingi ez'obuteesiba ez'okunaaba engalo ng'amazzi g'omu kkuuti n'amasavu tegaliiwo. Ng'ekyokulabirako, mu nsi ezikyakula waliwo amazzi agafuluma okuva mu kasumbi oba mu kasumbi akaaliko ebikonde n'akozesa enkumbi bwe kiba kyetaagisa. Mu mbeera ng'amazzi gabulako (ng'omu masomero oba mu byalo mu nsi ezikyakula), waliwo engeri ez'okutereka amazzi, gamba nga  tippy-taps n'engeri endala ez'obuteesiba.
Tippy-tap tekinologiya mwangu era akozesa ensuwa ey'amazzi ng'eyimiriddwa ku muggo, n'omugoba oguyamba okuyiwa amazzi ku mikono n'omugaati gw'amasavu.
Okuwummuza engalo obulungi kitundu kikulu mu buyonjo bw'engalo, naye engeri esingayo obulungi ey'okuwummulamu engalo mu kaabuyonjo ya bantu bonna yeeyo ey'okuwakana.
Okunoonyereza okw'amaanyi kulaga nti obugoye bw'ebitooke bwa buyonjo okusinga obugoye obukozesebwa mu kaabuyonjo.
Mu 2008, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa ekitongole ky'ebipapula ebiggya, European Tissue Symposium, kwaliko ku yunivasite ya Westminster mu London, okugeraageranya obuyonjo obuli mu nsawo, ebikozesebwa mu kumalira engalo n'ebikozesebwa mu kuyonja engalo.
Oluvannyuma lw'okunaaba n'okukalira engalo mu kyuma ekikalu, kyazuulibwa nti obuwumbi bw'obulwadde bwa bacterio bukula buli lukya ku buli kikumi 194 ku buli kikumi ku biwaawaatiro by'engalo n'ebitundu 254 ku buli kikumi ku mikono.
Okuwummuza engalo n'omukka gwaleetedde obuwumbi 42 ku buli kikumi bw'ebirwadde ku mikono n'ebitundu 15 ku buli kikumi ku mikono.
Oluvannyuma lw'okunaaba n'okukaza engalo n'ekitoffaali, obuwumbi bw'ebika bya buwuka bukendeera ku bungi bwa 76 ku buli kikumi ku bisenge n'okutuuka ku 77 ku buli kikumi ku mikono. Bannasayansi era baakola ebigezo okulaba oba waliwo obusobozi bw'okusannyalala n'abakozesa kaabuyonjo abalala n'obutonde bw'omu kaabuyonjo okusinziira ku ngeri buli ngeri ey'okukalamu.
Ekimera ekisalira engalo ekikola ng'omukka, ekikubira omukka okuva mu kyuma ku sipiidi ez'obubonero ez'emitwalo 180/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), kisobola okugoba obuwuka okuva mu ngalo n'ekikozesebwa era ne busobola okutabula abantu abalala abali mu kaabuyonjo n'ebitundu eby'omu kaabuyonjo mu bitundu eby'obuwanvu bwa ffuuti nga 2.
Okukozesa ekyuma ekikalira omukka ekisobozesa obuwuka obutonotono okusaasaana ku mayiro 0.25 okuva ku kyuma ekikalira omukka.
Empeereza z'ebitabo zaalaga nti tewaaliwo kusaasaanya kwa mikkaati. Mu 2005, okunoonyereza okwakolebwa TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, kwalaga engeri ez'enjawulo ez'okukalira engalo.
Oluvannyuma lw'okukaza engalo, enkyukakyuka zino wammanga mu bungi bw'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe zaalabikira:
Waliwo abazannyi bangi ab'ebyuma ebikalira engalo, era ebyuma ebikalira engalo bifaananiddwa n'okukalira n'ebitooke.
