LL angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme ekwatagana n'ebitundu eby'ebweru (ebisenge by'amasero) eby'amasero mu biwundu, emisona, omutima, ensigo n'ebisenge.
ACE2 erwanyisa ebikolwa bya enzyme ey'okukyusa angiotensin (ACE) ng'ekendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin II n'okwongera ku Ang (1-7) ekireetera eddagala eryo okuba ery'omugaso mu kujjanjaba endwadde z'omutima. ACE2 era y'ekifo ekirala ekituuka ku butoffaali bwa korona.
Enzimu ey'omu bantu etera okuyitibwa hACE2.
Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 y'ensulo ya zinc eri ku ntikko y'obutoffaali bw'ensiri n'obutoffaali obulala.
Protein ACE2 erimu ekitundu kya peptidase M2 ekikomekkereza N n'ekitundu kya collectrin ekikomekkereza C.
LACE2 ye protein eya type I ey'olukalala lw'ebitundu eby'ensiri, erina ekitundu ekikola ku by'ensiri ku bitundu by'omubiri eby'omu mawuggwe n'ebitundu ebirala.
