Omulimu ogusinga obukulu ogwa ACE2 kwe kusasulira ACE.
ACE esobola okugabanyaamu akawuka akayitibwa angiotensin I ne kayitibwa angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo ekwata ku amino acid eyitibwa carboxyl-terminated phenylamine eya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) era n'egikendeeza ne gifuuka angiotensin ey'okusaasaanya omusaayi (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 era esobola okugabanyaamu peptide endala ezitali zimu omuli [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, ne ghrelin.
LACE2 era ekakasa nti omutambuze wa SLC6A19 atambula bulungi era nga y'ekireeta obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'ekimera ekirimu obutoffaali obuyita mu bulago, ACE2 y'esinga okuyingira mu butoffaali bwa korona, omuli HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (akawuka akaviirako SARS); ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akaviirako COVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, okukwata ku protein ya SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 S1 eya spicules ku kitundu kya ACE2 ekya enzymatic ku maaso g'ensulo kivaamu endocytosis n'okusengula obuwuka ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu nsolo.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira nayo yeetaagisa protein S okutandikibwawo TMPRSS2 serine protease, okuziyiza kwe kati kunoonyerezaako ng'obujjanjabi obusobola okuvvuunuka obulwadde buno, ekireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2 mu bulabe bw'obulwadde buno.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'emikono n'ebitongole ebikuuma ddembe bingi bikubiriza okweyongera n'obujjanjabi obw'ekika ekya bulijjo nga tukozesa ACE inhibitor ne ARB.
Okunoonyereza n'okunoonyereza okwakolebwa nga July 11, 2012 kwalaga nti  okukozesa ACE inhibitors kwaleetawo okukendeeza okw'amaanyi kwa 34% mu kabi k'obulwadde bwa kkansa bw'omulembe bw'omubiri bw'ogeraageranya n'abo abataalina kkansa. 
Ate era,  akabi k'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe era kaakendeeranga mu balwadde abajjanjabibwa eddagala eriyitibwa ACE inhibitor abaalina akabi k'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, naddala abalwadde b'obulwadde bw'amasasi n'omutima okulemererwa.
Okukozesa ACE inhibitors era kwaleetanga okukendeeza ku kufa okuva mu kirwadde kya pneumonia, wadde nga ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza byali tebikakasa nnyo ng'okwo okwaliwo ku bulabe bwa kirwadde kya pneumonia.
Enzimu eyitibwa human recombinant angiotensin 2 converting enzyme (rhACE2) erina essuubi ery'okuyamba mu kujjanjaba obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'amawuggwe era kirabika eteekawo okulongoosa mu by'omusaayi n'okusaasaanya omukka mu mbizzi ezirina obulwadde bw'omukka oguyitibwa lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
RhACE2 ekwata ku bantu ekwata ku bantu ekwata ku bantu okumala essaawa nga 10 era ekikola okumala eddakiika 30 ng'oggyeko essaawa 24.
Ebizuuliddwa bingi biraga nti rhACE2 esobola okuba eddagala eryasuubizibwa eri abantu abatamanyi kugumiikiriza eddagala eriyitibwa renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAIs) oba eri endwadde ezirimu okufuluma kwa high angiotensin II. RhACE2 ey'okufukibwa mu mazzi erina okwekeberebwa mu bujjanjabi bw'obulwadde bw'obutafuna mutawaana mu mpumu.
Enkola za COVID-19 zikozesebwa ku ssimu ezikozesebwa mu kulondoola abantu mu kiseera kya kawumpuli wa coronavirus 2019-20, kwe kugamba, okumanya abantu (abo abazze bakwatagana) abayinza okuba nga baakwatagana n'omuntu alina obulwadde.
Enkola ez'enjawulo zaakuziddwa oba zaaweebwa, nga zikkiriziddwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu n'obuyinza.
Ebizimbe bingi byatandikibwawo okutondawo enkola z'okunoonya abakwatagana.
Enkola zino, naddala ezo ezisinziira ku kunoonyereza ku kifo abakozesa programu we babeera, zireetawo ebibuuzo ebikwata ku bukuumi.
Waliwo enkola endala ezitaali za maanyi, nga okukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika obusemberero bw'omukozesa ne ssimu endala.
Nga 10 Apuli 2020, Google ne Apple baategeezezza nti bagenda kussaawo enkola ey'okuyamba programu za Bluetooth mu nkola zaabwe ez'okuweereza Android ne iOS.
Gavumenti ya China, ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, etandisewo programu mu China esobozesa abantu okukebera oba nga baatuukiddwako omuntu alina COVID-19.
Ekikozesebwa mu bibuga ebisukka mu 200 mu China, ate Singapore yasalawo okukozesa programu eyitibwa TraceTogether.
Kyatandikibwawo ekibiina ky'abantu abakugu mu kompyuta era kyaweebwayo nga ekikye era kijja kuweebwa gavumenti. North Macedonia yatandikawo  StopKorona! , programu ya Bluetooth ekakasa abantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi era n'eyogera n'ab'obuyinza mu bwangu.
App eno yateekebwawo minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'obukugu ne minisitule y'ebyobulamu.
Nga 14 Apuli 2020, programu yali esembedde okukkirizibwa ku Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Nga 12 omwezi gwa Apuli, gavumenti yagamba nti enkola ey'okunoonyereza ku bantu gye yali akozesa yali mu mitendera egy'okusingawo era nti esobola okutandikibwawo mu wiiki eziddako. Enkola y'emu eteekeddwa okukozesebwa mu Ireland ne Bufalansa ( StopCovid).
Australia ne New Zealand ziteekateeka okutandikawo programu ez'engeri ya TraceTogether mu Singapore era nga zisinziira ku nkola ya BlueTrace. Russia eteekateeka okutandikawo programu ey'okunoonya abantu abalina obulwadde bwa COVID-19 era nga babeera mu Moscow, okukakasa nti tebasimbula maka gaabwe.
Ross Anderson, Profesa wa by'obunjiniya mu byokwerinda mu yunivasite ya Cambridge, yayogerako ku bizibu bingi ebiyinza okubaawo mu kukozesa enkola eziriko enkola, omuli obulimba n'obutaba na mugaso singa abantu batono nnyo abakozesa enkola.
Olw'okweraliikirira ku kusaasaana kwa programu ez'obulimba oba ez'akabi ezikwata ku coronavirus, Apple ekkiriza ebitongole ebikakafu oba ebyesigika okwongera ku programu ezikwata ku coronavirus ku App Store.
Google ne Amazon nabyo byateekawo amateeka ge gamu.
