Baayagala okufulumya eddagala erisobola okugezesebwa ku bantu mu nnaku 90 zokka.
Nga Maaki 5, 2020, Washington University e St. Louis yalangirira enteekateeka y'okukulaakulanya eddagala.
Nga Maaki 5, 2020, Ekitongole kya Amerika eky'Obujjanjabi n'Eby'okukozesa mu Kufuuyira Abasibe mu Fort Detrick ne Walter Reed Army Institute of Research mu Silver Spring, zombi eziri mu bugwanjuba bwa Maryland, zaalangirira nti zikola ku ddagala.
