Nga 17 Maaki 2020 mu Italy, Takis Biotech, kkampuni y'omu Italy ekola eby'obujjanjabi, yalangirira nti ejja kuba n'ebivudde mu kukebera eddagala mu Apuli 2020 era nti okugezesa abantu ku ddagala eryasembayo okuteekebwamu kuyinza okutandika mu ttoggo.
Mu Bufalansa, nga 19 Maaki 2020, ekibiina kya Coalition for Epidemic Preparedness Innovations (CEPI) kyalangirira okusigaza obukadde bwa US$ 4.9 mu kibiina ekikola ku kunoonyereza ku ddagala lya COVID-19 nga mwe muli Institut Pasteur, Themis Bioscience (Vienna, Austria) ne yunivasite ya Pittsburgh, ekireetawo obuwumbi bwa US$ 29 mu ssente eza CEPI mu kunoonyereza ku ddagala lya COVID-19.
Ab'omukago abalala aba ECPI abakola mu by'ensimbi mu kukuza eddagala erigema COVID-19 be Moderna, Curevac, Inovio, Novavax, Yunivasite ya Hong Kong, Yunivasite ya Oxford, ne Yunivasite ya Queensland.
Nga Maaki 20, 2020, ab'obuyinza mu by'obulamu mu Russia baalangirira nti bannasayansi baatandise okugezesa ebisolo ku bulwadde mukaaga obw'enjawulo.
Abanoonyereza ku Imperial College London balangiridde nga Maaki 20, 2020 nti bakola eddagala erikolera ku RNA erigenda mu maaso okulwanyisa COVID-19.
