Ensigo ezirwanyisa SARS ne MERS zagezeseddwa ku bisolo ebitali bantu.
Mu 2020, tewali ddagala liwonya oba likuuma ku SARS eriraze obukuumi n'obwanguzi mu bantu.
Okusinziira ku biwandiiko by'okunoonyereza ebyafulumizibwa mu 2005 ne 2006, okumanya n'okuzimba eddagala eriggya n'eddagala okujjanjaba SARS byali bya muwendo nnyo eri gavumenti n'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu mu nsi yonna. Tewali ddagala liyinza kukakasibwa ku MERS.
MERS bwe yeeyongera okusaasaana, kyatwalibwa nti okunoonyereza okwaliwo ku SARS kwali kusobola okuteekebwawo okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa MERS-CoV.
Mu Maaki 2020, eddagala limu lyokka erirwanyisa MERS (eryesigamiziddwa ku DNA) lyaggwaako okunoonyereza ku bantu mu kitundu eky'okusatu era eddala ssatu zaali mu nkola; eddagala lyonna lyaliko ekirwadde kya siriimu, bibiri byaliko ekirwadde kya adenovirusi (ChAdOx1-MERS, BVRS-GamVac) ate ekirala kyaliko ekirwadde kya MVA (MVA-MERS-S).
Ebitabo ku mikutu gy'empuliziganya byafulumya endowooza nti akawuka akaviirako COVID-19 kaali kamanyiddwa era nti eddagala lyali lirabika dda.
