Enkola endala nga benzalkonium chloride ne chlorhexidine gluconate (ekimera ekirongoosa obulwadde) tezirina mugaso. Mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu Hong Kong, ebibala by'amalusu byaggibwa ku lunaku lumu oluvannyuma lw'okutwalibwa mu ddwaliro.
